remarks.format: ## Remarks 配置文件是完全 .NET Framework 的子集。A profile is a subset of the full .NET Framework. 例如，.NET Framework 客户端配置文件是 .NET Framework 3.5 Service Pack 1 的子集，而 .NET Framework 4 客户端配置文件是 .NET Framework 4.5 的子集。For example, the .NET Framework Client Profile is a subset of the .NET Framework 3.5 Service Pack 1, and the .NET Framework 4 Client Profile is a subset of the .NET Framework 4.5. 有关详细信息，请参阅 [.NET Framework Client Profile](/dotnet/framework/deployment/client-profile)。For more information, see [.NET Framework Client Profile](/dotnet/framework/deployment/client-profile).
